ckground with integrity, honesty, and professionalism suitable for government security position with public trust responsibilities"}','{"access_control","surveillance_monitoring","incident_response"}','2024-01-21','2024-02-21'),
        ('Event Coordinator','Plan and organize government events and community meetings. Coordinate logistical arrangements for successful event execution.','As an Event Coordinator for Lideta Subcity Government Office, you will be responsible for planning, organizing, and executing a wide range of government events, community meetings, public consultations, and official ceremonies that facilitate citizen engagement and government communication. Your role encompasses every aspect of event management from initial concept development and logistical planning through on-site coordination and post-event evaluation. You will work with various government departments to identify event requirements, develop budgets, select venues, coordinate vendors, and manage all operational details to ensure successful outcomes. This position requires exceptional organizational skills, creativity, and ability to work under pressure while managing multiple events simultaneously. You will engage with diverse stakeholders including government officials, community leaders, service providers, and the public, requiring diplomacy, cultural sensitivity, and problem-solving abilities. Additionally, you will develop event protocols, evaluation mechanisms, and improvement strategies to enhance the quality and impact of government-sponsored events in serving Lideta community needs.','Lideta Community Center',45000,'fulltime','Event','{"Plan and coordinate all logistical aspects of government events including community meetings, public consultations, official ceremonies, training workshops, and cultural celebrations from conception to completion","Develop comprehensive event plans, timelines, budgets, and checklists for each event, identifying requirements, responsibilities, and contingency plans for potential challenges","Coordinate venue selection, setup arrangements, equipment rental, catering services, transportation, accommodations, and other vendor services according to event specifications and